data.description: Nothing to do but unpack and move right in! Beautiful open floor plan offers loads of updates, including new roof, new A/C, new water heater, all new Stainless appliances new tile walls in guest bath, new floors, and freshly painted throughout including garage and floors! You will love this resort living with pool, clubhouse, basketball and so mych more. Barrwood development is close to everything, restaurants, shops and turnpike.
